{"tid":417310,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］《爆足一周》復播","createTime":"2017-09-28T14:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T11:40:52.000Z","uid":5812,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"81645d40b06c8d68c6899ad57fe36dddaf228e1f","tid":417310,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《爆足一周》四集腰斬 <br />\n<br />\n在2012年10月底第四集播出之前，另一主持人莊思敏在微博上說「今晚10點爆足一週。。。保証你，今晚有嘢爆，唔睇就後悔嘞。。」最終，在第四集的尾聲，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">查小欣親自宣布會虛心聆聽觀眾意見，徹底檢討，調整節目內容，在2013年初再與大家見面，即變相宣布節目遭即時腰斬</span></span>，而到了2013年初，《爆足一周》也沒有任何復播的消息，可見此節目已壽終正寢。《爆足一周》原定製作13集，現在僅得4集便叫停，被指是最「短命」節目之一。網民對無綫從善如流將節目腰斬感高興，又對節目及查小欣強烈恥笑。另外，網民對節目結束後莊思敏在「熄咪」後直接問「係咪即係腰斬呀？」及之後各主持的「O嘴」表情加以討論 。<br />\n<br />\n2018都就來黎，幾時復播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5116356f1bb8e51cc3e1c65ff600d02e25fa403f","tid":417310,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住小欣姐"},{"pid":"13e8949ee360414b150762dedb06895a7ac285a4","tid":417310,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507c74b6b3311c82e3b26f65144727712bff9958","tid":417310,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcf746f9faae0015d6c905550167038c35d662b","tid":417310,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as